function Why()
  while turtle.detect() do
  turtle.dig()
  os.sleep(0.5)
 end
 turtle.forward()
 while turtle.detectDown() or turtle.detectUp() do
   turtle.digUp()
   turtle.digDown()
  end
 end 
  
    
 function placeTorch()
   turtle.down()
   turtle.back() 
   turtle.select(16)
   turtle.placeUp()
   turtle.forward()
   turtle.up()
end
  
 local run = 0
 local j = 0
 local k = 0
 
 term.write(" Branch length: ")
 run = read()
 
 for i= 1, run do
   k = i - 1
   j = k % 10
   if j == 1 then
    placeTorch() 
      end 
     Why()
 end
 
 turtle.select(16)
 turtle.placeUp()
 turtle.turnRight()
 turtle.turnRight()
 
   for i = 1, run do
   turtle.down()
   turtle.forward()
end
